overview: Another winning recipe in the critically-acclaimed Sweet Cream Pie series. You’ll be craving a piece of the ‘100% All-Internal Cum Shot’ pie, as these cum-starved cuties are taking shots of creamy filling in every hole! Don’t be fooled by imitations - we promise 100% real organic cream filling in ever pie! Sweet Cream Pies 5 is a ‘must stock’ item for your Cream Pie section!
title: Sweet Cream Pies 5
